title: NuFACE Facial Toning Device at Home Spa Treatment
description:
Lisa Kasanicky, creator of ArizonaSpaGirls.com, talks about her favorite microcurrent facial toning device. 

Learn more about NuFACE: http://bit.ly/AboutNuFACE  

NuFACE, the innovator of clinically proven, at-home anti-aging devices uses the power of microccurent technology to tone and lift your facial muscles without plastic surgery and facelifts. Carol Cole the founder and famed aesthetician had a vision to create a handheld device that would utilize microcurrent technology for anyone who wanted to take anti-aging into their own hands.
